%% Server 상태머신 (CONTEXT.md "Server 상태" 절)
%% internal/server의 상태 enum과 1:1 일치
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> STOPPED
    STOPPED --> STARTING: StartServer()
    STARTING --> RUNNING: child spawned + port bound
    STARTING --> PORT_COLLISION: pre-start port check fail
    STARTING --> ERROR: spawn fail
    RUNNING --> STOPPING: StopServer()
    RUNNING --> ERROR: child exit unexpected
    STOPPING --> STOPPED: Triple-Pass complete
    STOPPING --> ERROR: kill ultimately failed
    PORT_COLLISION --> STARTING: user accepts §2.6 wizard (force kill or reassign)
    PORT_COLLISION --> STOPPED: user cancels
    ERROR --> STOPPED: user dismiss
    ERROR --> STARTING: user retry

    note right of STARTING
        Buttons disabled during STARTING/STOPPING.
        No queuing, no cancellation.
    end note
